ting localities are indicated on maps and in the text, and collecting methods are expertly described. Of particular interest to students and geologists for its bibliography and synthesis of heretofore widely scattered information, this abundantly illustrated book can be read by student and layman alike as a comprehensive introduction to the fascinating geology of Michigan.\u003cbr\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://doi.org/10.3998/mpub.23827\"\u003eView on Fulcrum platform.\u003c\/a\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e","identifier":"https://doi.org/10.3998/mpub.23827","language":"eng","modified":"2025-08-16T08:24:12Z","published":"1970-01-01","publisher":"University of Michigan Press","subject":["Michigan and the Great Lakes:Nature","Nature/Environment"]},"links":[{"rel":"self","href":"https://www.fulcrum.org/ebooks/f1881q25t/download","type":"application/epub+zip"},{"rel":"http://opds-spec.org/acquisition/open-access","href":"https://www.fulcrum.org/ebooks/f1881q25t/download","type":"application/epub+zip"},{"rel":"http://opds-spec.org/acquisition/open-access","href":"https://www.fulcrum.org/ebooks/n583xz16k/download","type":"application/pdf"}],"images":[{"href":"https://www.fulcrum.org//image-service/th83m293m/full/full/0/default.jpg","type":"image/jpeg"},{"href":"https://www.fulcrum.org//image-service/th83m293m/full/200,/0/default.jpg","width":200,"type":"image/jpeg"},{"href":"https://www.fulcrum.org//image-service/th83m293m/full/400,/0/default.jpg","width":400,"type":"image/jpeg"},{"href":"https://www.fulcrum.org//image-service/th83m293m/full/800,/0/default.jpg","width":800,"type":"image/jpeg"}]},{"metadata":{"@type":"http://schema.org/EBook","title":"On the Current Situation in the Ukraine","author":["Mazlakh, Serhii","Mazlakh, Serhii","Shakhrai, Vasyl'","Shakhrai, Vasyl","Shakhrai, Vasyl","Potichnyj, Peter J.","Potichnyj, Peter","Luther, Michael M."],"description":"\u003cdiv\u003eThe struggle for national liberation, the freedom to develop an independent identity—these are the iss